{"tid":917562,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"假設飛機上有一個中國婦女","createTime":"2018-11-26T13:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T15:52:17.000Z","uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa753263b6c1832c187fceb5592a4d8111afc28d","tid":917562,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"假設往中國的一班飛機上<br />\n<br />\n有個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n婦女私自調位，香港人同佢理論。<br />\n事後 香港人講<br />\n<br />\n有啲人種寧舍麻煩，<br />\n<br />\n但港男覺得會歧視講成<br />\n<br />\n有啲人寧舍麻煩，<br />\n<br />\n但港男又覺得會歧視所以改<br />\n<br />\n她真麻煩，<br />\n<br />\n但港男又想起社會，(她)可能是歧視女，又改成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真麻煩，大概這不包含任何歧視成份。<br />\n<br />\n港男大叫 真麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n中國婦女表示:「你不也是中國人。」<br />\n<br />\n於是港男下一步的選擇又更難。<br />\n<br />\n「收聲啦，死蝗蟲。」唔得<br />\n「你老母邊個同你係中國人。」<br />\n「I come from HK 咁樣講又未免太低質。」<br />\n「於是港男一句收中國婦女皮。<br />\n<br />\n大家估下係啲咩 好簡單"},{"pid":"c5daa9c7933030dcbbcf0625d5cc2a7c64fe3fb5","tid":917562,"uid":213300,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/212434_982ce03839522e4ed602cc4c7a4de7d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F212434_982ce03839522e4ed602cc4c7a4de7d8.jpg&h=3df524cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40967b3b71bb6a2370b263cd3d8f33e4de403032","tid":917562,"uid":15406,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:25:18.000Z","msg":"你up乜"},{"pid":"f0ee0759f12a2f03a65103eed2d602331c8eb992","tid":917562,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"0b4d0749b1f86c25ab7b69cc746fd360bbf1bd0f","tid":917562,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"請做個良好中國人？"},{"pid":"45db1728a9a9edc2d80f1e6d5d6265db893e45b3","tid":917562,"uid":30098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:26:59.000Z","